dct_title_s: A map of North America: with the European settlements & whatever else is remarkable in ye West Indies, from the latest and best observations; R. W. Seale delin. et sculp.
dct_description_sm: Relief shown pictorially. Shows California as an island. Shows locations of European cities and towns, Indian towns, forts and castles.
